thread.title: Kristen LaCosse
thread.title_full: Peaches Boutique reviewed by Kristen LaCosse

author: Kristen LaCosse
title: Kristen LaCosse
text: Honestly I was skeptical about shopping here because it had this vibe that it was really expensive, but once I got there I realized that they are actually reasonablely priced for great dresses! I had such a fun time and I found an amazing prom dress that I can't wait to wear. I wish I visited for other dances!
